    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/e109dde0b4668e1f704384afdf67956f.avif?t=1726965877\" width=622 height=108 /></span><br><br><strong>欢迎来到封建日本，一个充满武士和危险的世界。在这个世界中，你将扮演一只青蛙武士，任务是打败蛇族并结束战争。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/67889b7f1aa88141e4941f3fa2988cfc.poster.avif?t=1726965877\" width=622 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/67889b7f1aa88141e4941f3fa2988cfc.webm?t=1726965877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/67889b7f1aa88141e4941f3fa2988cfc.mp4?t=1726965877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>你的敏捷和速度将在跳过障碍、攀爬墙壁和天花板、以及穿越传送门时得到测试。利用你的智慧用钥匙打开锁并使用蹦床跳得更快。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/c9632f219cf76f0a976aa992b78ecfab.poster.avif?t=1726965877\" width=622 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/c9632f219cf76f0a976aa992b78ecfab.webm?t=1726965877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/c9632f219cf76f0a976aa992b78ecfab.mp4?t=1726965877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>但要小心：蛇不会轻易放弃。你需要发挥青蛙的所有技能来打败它们并拯救你的王国。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215500/extras/53117b2c8d5130fcfc8f6ce0a9ec6d8e.poster.avif?t=1726965877\" width=622 height=260 ><source src=\"http